三月の水<br />Joao Gilberto</a></h4><p>シンプルなる「美」が静かに迫り来る名盤。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000VZE0F0?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000VZE0F0" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', '三月の水-Joao Gilberto']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/jp/album/joao-gilberto/id14522599?uo=4&at=10lcnA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', '三月の水-Joao Gilberto']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/09/paris-texas.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/paristexas.jpg" alt="Paris, Texas / Ry Cooder" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2011/09/paris-texas.php">Paris, Texas<br />Ry Cooder</a></h4><p>ライ・クーダのギターが切なく、また蜃気楼のように幻想的に響く。真夏に涼しい部屋で冷えた飲み物を片手に聞いていると贅沢な気持ちになる。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005HGRN/ref=as_li_tf_tl?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005HGRN" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Paris, Texas-Ry Cooder']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fparis-texas%252Fid358238100%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Paris, Texas-Ry Cooder']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/12/african-mode-plus.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/africanmode.jpg" alt="African Mode / Bajune Tobeta" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a hre