/a></h4><p>「一音」「一音」が透明感に溢れ宝石のように輝く美しさ。ドビュッシーのピアノで彼以上のピアノを聞いたことがない。ある意味ドビュッシー以上にドビュッシーな世界。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000YY66JQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000YY66JQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Debussy: Preludes (I); Images-Arturo Benedetti Michelangeli']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpreludes-book-1-8-la-fille%252Fid42278067%253Fi%253D42278100%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D3" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Debussy: Preludes (I); Images-Arturo Benedetti Michelangeli']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

